==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wardian
<hw>Ward"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Designating, or
pertaining to, a kind of glass inclosure for keeping ferns, mosses,
etc., or for transporting growing plants from a distance; <as>as, a
<ex>Wardian</ex> case of plants</as>; -- so named from the inventor,
Nathaniel B. <etsep>Ward</etsep>, an Englishman.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wardmote</ent>⟦br⟧
